reviewText: I gave this one a shot since I'm a fan of Rosalba Neri. I thought it was pretty funny and worth the price (though for the price, you'd think you were getting a Blu-Ray). If Italian comedies ain't your cup of tea, don't bother with this one. Chances are, if you're on this page, you have an idea of what these movies are about. You're not likely to find this on Netflix, Amazon Instant, or most other sites that legally stream movies.
